| Column | Used by Trader for |
|--------|-------------------|
| sia_sentiment | Signal 1 (Social) in composite — replaces raw social score |
| sia_narrative_intensity | Narrative momentum signal (Signal 3 partial) |
| sia_platform_divergence | Platform divergence classification |
| sia_divergence_bonus | Added to composite score |
| sia_mention_count_24h | Mention volume gate (< 50 → penalize) |
| sia_top_accounts | Displayed in status output |
| sia_updated_at | Staleness check |
| data_available | partial_data flag on trade entry |

